Various tools for extending JUnit functionality

v0.7
 - Can launch a JPanel or Canvas directly
 - JTestFrame can accept a title
v0.6
 - JTestFrame only packs if size not already set
 - Default wait time is 2 seconds
v0.5
 - Better mouse controls in JGraphicsPanel
 - JGraphicsPanel fully respects Swing drawing policy
 - Renamed JTestFrame #start() to #run()
